name: Kon-Tiki Superhero S1#34
description:
Kon-Tiki Superhero is a fictional character. IT by profession, hero by passion. Martial arts and bodybuilding expert. Cigar aficionado. Self made, enjoying life of independence. Follow his adventures via NFT collections and comic book coming soon.
Kon-Tiki Superhero S1 represent first NFT collection, name "Origin". This collection is featuring 50 items, 12 copies each. Enjoy Kon-Tiki adventures.
